  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Identify Pilot Project&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    There are some criteria to consider for selecting a pilot project. These include:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Choosing the emphasis for the pilot&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li style=&quot;LIST-STYLE-TYPE: none&quot;>&#xD;
        &lt;ul>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Focus on process refinement&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Focus on tool selection validation&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Focus on metrics validation&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
            &lt;li>&#xD;
                Focus on skill building&#xD;
            &lt;/li>&#xD;
        &lt;/ul>&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Choose the domain within the organization to focus&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Consider the organization's reuse/asset maturity&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Evaluate the impact to the organization&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Below is a sample outline of a pilot and the major tasks for the pilot. The focus of this sample is on process&#xD;
    refinement.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
